    <item>
      <title>贷款业务回落影响信用卡收入，NerdWallet 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/nerdwallet-falls-as-lending-pullback-hurts-credit-card-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NerdWallet Inc. 由于发卡机构收紧贷款而导致其主要信用卡收入下降，尽管国际扩张和新的人工智能产品预计将有助于今年晚些时候恢复增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/nerdwallet-falls-as-lending-pullback-hurts-credit-card-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 17:05:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷集团表示正在考虑 Tamko 的选择，包括出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/carlyle-group-said-to-mull-options-for-tamko-including-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，凯雷投资集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 和 Tamko Building Products 的家族所有者正在考虑出售，这可能会使这家屋顶瓦制造商的估值超过 35 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/carlyle-group-said-to-mull-options-for-tamko-including-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 16:59:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保时捷利润因车型更新和中国经济低迷而下滑 30%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/porsche-profit-slumps-30-on-model-renewals-china-downturn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保时捷公司第一季度利润大幅下滑，创下自 2022 年 9 月上市以来的最弱业绩，原因是车型更换和中国需求疲软打压了该制造商的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/porsche-profit-slumps-30-on-model-renewals-china-downturn</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市政监管机构指出购买“Build America”债券的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/muni-regulator-warns-about-risks-of-buying-build-america-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市政债券市场的监管机构发布了一份说明，强调了购买交易价格超过 100 美分的“建设美国债券”的风险，随着政府越来越多地在再融资下回购这些债券，投资者将面临潜在损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/muni-regulator-warns-about-risks-of-buying-build-america-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 14:06:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着交易员在关键通胀数据中找到缓解，债券溃败有所缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/treasury-yields-fall-after-pce-inflation-data-meet-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五美国国债抛售暂停，收益率从年内最高水平回落，此前通胀报告缓解了人们对一系列高于预期价格数据的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/treasury-yields-fall-after-pce-inflation-data-meet-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 12:41:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
