      <title>英国因“精心策划的恶意活动”召见俄罗斯特使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/uk-men-charged-under-new-security-law-over-pro-russia-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国周五传唤了俄罗斯大使，此前警方早些时候根据新的国家安全法指控几名男子支持俄罗斯，在英国领土上纵火袭击一家与乌克兰有关的企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/uk-men-charged-under-new-security-law-over-pro-russia-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 12:09:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
